imdb.plot outline: Traveling across all 50 states capturing the product development and creation by American artists, craftsmen, carpenters, jewelers, wineries and breweries. Our celebrity hostess will be coached through the processes while making the products first hand as America tunes in. Intellectual property rights are intertwined with this film production.
